item.title: Autoing on games where
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

[quote=“Bobby, post:1, topic:144134”]you can trade the gold for real moeny.

does this work? since it would be pretty sweet to auto for real money. has anyone tried? or do they have any expeiarnce with this also what games would work?[/quote]
What do you think? There are two reasons to cheat in a game: levels (mind you, you better hope your account doesn’t get caught before you reach desired levels), or in-game currency, which can then be sold for actual money.

Most people would probably do the latter, at least in the case of RS, seeing as it’s extremely hard to avoid being caught and banned.
However there’s a lot of chinese people that farm gold and sell it, so thats nowhere near as valuable as it used to be.
